This is Perl module Mojolicious::Plugin::Directory::Stylish.

INSTALLATION

Mojolicious::Plugin::Directory::Stylish installation is straightforward. If
your CPAN shell is set up, you should just be able to do

    % cpan Mojolicious::Plugin::Directory::Stylish

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

Mojolicious::Plugin::Directory::Stylish documentation is available as in POD.
So you can do:

    % perldoc Mojolicious::Plugin::Directory::Stylish

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

